'''Delta Base''', also known as the '''Suolriep Sector HQ''', was a remote [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] base on [[New Kisge]], the eighth moon of [[Chaasch]] in [[Suolriep sector/Legends|Suolriep sector]]. It was established by [[General/Legends|General]] [[Vanden Willard/Legends|Vanden Willard]], with [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Tole Warren]] as one of his top officers.<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

It was named because of famed [[Delta Unit]], from [[Scandium Team]].

Rebels [[Mors Odrion]]<ref name="SOSR">''[[Secrets of the Sisar Run]]''</ref> and [[Rekara]] were assigned to Delta Base soon after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]]. Former Scandium Team leader [[Harovan Toth]] also went to Delta Base after semi-retiring, to work as patrol [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]]<ref name="J11">{{JournalCite|11|Cracken's Rebel Operatives (article)}}</ref>. After the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]], [[Tal-Yannar Najjan]] was assigned as a [[Medic/Legends|medic]] to this base.

